<div class="about-us-container">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>Welcome to Alpha Gym – where strength meets passion. Our mission is to empower individuals on their fitness journey, fostering a community dedicated to achieving health and wellness goals.</p>

    <p>At Alpha Gym, we provide a dynamic and inclusive fitness environment, offering state-of-the-art facilities and expert trainers. Whether you're a fitness enthusiast or a beginner, our diverse range of classes and personalized training sessions cater to all levels.</p>

    <p>Why Choose Alpha Gym:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><span class="highlight">Expert Trainers:</span> Our certified trainers are committed to guiding and supporting you in reaching your fitness goals.</li>
        <li><span class="highlight">Community:</span> Join our fitness family, where camaraderie and encouragement fuel every workout.</li>
        <li><span class="highlight">Variety of Classes:</span> From high-energy group classes to one-on-one coaching, we offer options to keep your fitness routine engaging.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Embark on the journey to a stronger, healthier you with Alpha Gym. We're not just a gym; we're a lifestyle that promotes health, happiness, and self-discovery.</p>
